Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Where is the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今無情一帯の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Here is no truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}栄光もなく奪い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It's like a party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}交錯する者たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突き進め果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}勝者と敗者どちらも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}maybe something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}What can I belive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そんな問いなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}No one answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:03:00.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すべてこの虚空の中消えてった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今はBREAK OUT BREAK OUT進めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:11.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}その意志を揚げて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあもっとBREAK OUT BREAK OUT世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:21.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}切り開け迷っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}So we gatta just go crazy,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}just go crazy now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}dance,dance crazy ,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢か地獄かGO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理何處尋覓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眼前這冷酷無情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理無從尋覓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}僅有骯髒的搶與奪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像一場派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}命運縱橫交錯的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向著終點一意前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無論勝者或敗者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}或許某物已然瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何物可信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此疑問為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無人作答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:03:00.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切盡皆消失在這片虛無之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}現在BREAK OUT BREAK OUT  前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:11.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高舉這份決心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}來吧  繼續BREAK OUT BREAK OUT突破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:21.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界的束縛  即使迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我們只需變得瘋狂  瘋而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如今只需變得瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舞蹈  舞至瘋狂  瘋而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢或地獄  GO CRY GO
